    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Spherical or circular objects with a pierced center, usually made of wood, stone, or clay, that act as a flywheel for a spindle and stop for the yarn.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
